        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Pragmata surpasses 1m copies sold in just two days]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/pragmata-surpasses-1m-copies-sold-in-two-days</link>
            <guid>1495969</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
      <article data-ads="true" data-article-type="news" data-article-group="news" data-paywalled="false" data-premium="false" data-sponsored="false" data-type="article">


<header data-component="article-header">
  

    


  <p>

  <figure>
      <picture>
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 2dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=3&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 3dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/Close-up-of-Diana-in-Pragmata.-She-has-blond-hair-and-blue-eyes.jpg?width=570&amp;quality=85&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=webp" media="(min-width: 550px) and (max-resolution: 2dppx)">
        
      </picture>

        <figcaption>
          <span>Image credit: <cite>Capcom</cite></span>
        </figcaption>
  </figure>
  </p>

    

</header>
  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>In just two days after release, Capcom's latest game - Pragmata - has surpassed 1m units sold.</p>
<p>The studio noted Capcom's space-based game was created by "primarily" a team of younger developers, who "created an innovative gameplay experience by fusing action gameplay with puzzle elements set within a distinctive world ruled over by artificial intelligence".</p>
<figure>
<div>
<p><span data-type="targeting">
<span>To see this content please enable targeting cookies.</span>
</span> </p>
</div>
<figcaption>Pragmata - Official 90-Second Overview Trailer. <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l5y-nnoLEpQ" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Watch on YouTube</a></figcaption>
</figure>
<p>Capcom added that given Pragmata was a totally new franchise for the studio, it "implemented a range of marketing" strategies to get word out there. This included a playable demo and support for <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/platforms/switch-2">Nintendo Switch 2</a>.</p>
<p>"As a result, these initiatives generated significant momentum, enabling Pragmata to achieve worldwide sales of over one million units in just two days despite being a completely new IP, marking a strong start for the title," <a href="https://www.capcom.co.jp/ir/english/news/html/e260420.html">Capcom said</a>.</p>
<p>"Capcom remains firmly committed to satisfying the expectations of all users by leveraging its industry leading game development capabilities in order to create highly entertaining gameplay experiences."</p>
<figure>
 


<figcaption><span>Image credit: <cite>Capcom</cite></span></figcaption>
</figure>
<p>Capcom has already had a stellar year. Along with Pragmata - <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/pragmata-review">a game our Dom awarded four stars in Eurogamer's review</a> - it also released <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/resident-evil-requiem-review">Resident Evil Requiem to high-praise back in February</a>. Meanwhile, there is <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/dragons-dogma-2-mysterious-patch-steam-rumoured-dlc">speculation that Capcom is gearing up to release some DLC for Dragon's Dogma 2</a>.</p><p>If you are currently playing Pragmata, but need an extra hand, be sure to check out our guides. Here is one on <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/pragmata-safe-box-locations">Pragmata's Safe Box locations</a>, and here is <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/pragmata-walkthrough-tips-guides">a more thorough walkthrough complete with useful tips</a> to get you going.</p>

        </div>

  
      </article>



  



  <div>
      <p>
        <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/pragmata">Pragmata</a>
      </p>

      <p>
            <span>PS5</span>, 
            <span>Xbox Series X/S</span>, 
            <span>PC</span>, 
            <span>Nintendo Switch 2</span>
      </p>





</div>

