  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>Windrose - the piratical survival game from Kraken Express - has shifted 1m copies in just six days.</p>
<p>The developer shared the latest milestone with a celebratory post, acknowledging the "crew of fine brave captains sailing the seas of Windrose" since <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/windrose-early-access-steam-positive-reviews">the game's widely-praised early access release last week</a>. It added that not only has the game moved 1m copies, but Windrose also welcomed 200,000 concurrent players.</p>

